> For you folks out where they have these places, how much does it cost?
>
> For instance, If I wanted to go out and pull an alternator off of a T4
> engine, would they quote a price before I pulled it? or just when I got
> ready to leave?

They normally have a board with all the parts prices posted.  This can be
a bonus for some aircooled parts, since a fan shroud (a relatively complex
part on an aircooled) is priced the same as the plastic radiator fan
shrouds on watercooled cars.

